[MUSIC PLAYING]

Variety is the slice of life. With an adjustable slicer shredder, S blade, and dough blade, the Breville Sous Chef 12 gives professional food prep results in seconds. Let's see it in action. Speed of a fruit processor combined with the precision of a professorial chef, the Sous Chef 12 brought to you by the food thinkers of Breville.
